Package: twostepAKSA
Type: Package
Title: Two-step Test for Predictive Biomarkers with Zero Inflation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Miles", "Xi", email = "nxi@ucla.edu", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Implements a two-step permutation test for continuous predictive
    biomarkers with zero inflation. Part A targets the spike at zero; Part B
    scans the positive tail using an Averaged Kolmogorovâ€“Smirnov Approach(AKSA).
    Includes Fisher and Brown combinations with permutation-calibrated p-values.
